Do you believe in witchcraft?

00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:50.236
Nicole: No.

00:06:50.260 --> 00:06:51.539
KB: Voodoo?
Nicole: No.

00:06:51.563 --> 00:06:53.928
KB: Things that go bump in the night?
Nicole: No.

00:06:53.952 --> 00:06:55.536
KB: Besides, who's next, no, OK.

00:06:55.560 --> 00:06:57.952
I want you to just stand
exactly like this for me,

00:06:57.976 --> 00:06:59.946
pull up your sleeves, if you don't mind.

00:06:59.970 --> 00:07:01.487
OK, now, I want you to be aware

00:07:01.511 --> 00:07:03.536
