00:07:11.760 --> 00:07:13.723
From this point onwards, close your eyes,

00:07:13.747 --> 00:07:15.568
do not say anything, do not open them,

00:07:15.592 --> 00:07:17.160
be aware of the sensations.

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:27.136
Yes or no, did you feel anything?

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:28.161
Nicole: Yes.

00:07:28.185 --> 00:07:30.198
KB: You did feel that? What did you feel?

00:07:30.222 --> 00:07:31.874
Nicole: A touch on my back.

00:07:31.898 --> 00:07:33.612
KB: How many times did you feel it?

00:07:35.412 --> 00:07:36.460
Nicole: Twice.

00:07:36.484 --> 00:07:39.150
KB: Twice. OK, extend your left arm
out in front of you.

00:07:39.174 --> 00:07:40.605
Extend your left arm, OK.

00:07:41.710 --> 00:07:43.136
OK, keep it there.

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:46.599
Be aware of the sensations, don't say
anything, don't open your eyes, OK.

00:07:55.136 --> 00:07:56.517
Did you feel anything, there?

00:07:56.541 --> 00:07:58.167
Nicole: Yes.
KB: What did you feel?

00:07:58.191 --> 00:07:59.223
Nicole: Three --

00:07:59.247 --> 00:08:01.270
KB: Like a tickling sensation?
Nicole: Yes.

00:08:01.294 --> 00:08:03.136
KB: Can you show us where?

00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:05.136
OK, excellent. Open your eyes.

00:08:05.160 --> 00:08:06.183
I never touched you.

00:08:06.207 --> 00:08:09.741
