00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:26.732
Can you take a seat
right over here, if you don't mind.

00:08:26.756 --> 00:08:27.907
Sit right here.
Man: OK.

00:08:28.629 --> 00:08:31.136
KB: OK, take a seat. Excellent, OK.

